[Nouns] edge, verge, brink, brow, brim, margin, border, confine, skirt, rim, flange, side, mouth; jaws, chops, chaps, fauces; lip, muzzle.
threshold, door, porch; portal (opening) [more]; coast, shore.
frame, fringe, flounce, frill, list, trimming, edging, skirting, hem, selvedge, welt, furbelow, valance.
[Adjectives] border, marginal, skirting; labial, labiated, marginated.
